page-index-meta-description: Ethereum na global decentralized platform for money and new new application. On this ethereum, you fit write code wey dey control money, and build different applications wey everybody for this world fit use.
page-index-description: Ethereum na di komunity-run technology wey dey ginga cryptocurrency ether (ETH) and plenti aplikashons wey dem disentralize.
page-index-get-started-description: ethereum.org na yor portal wey dey take yu enta Ethereum world. Di tech dey new and dey always show - im dey helep show pipol way. Dis na wetin we rekomend make yu do if yu wont enta am.

page-index-get-started-dapps-image-alt: Wi dey show one doge wey dey yus komputa.

page-index-what-is-ethereum-description: Ethereum na di technology wey bi haus for digital money, world payments, and aplikashons. Di komunity don build betta digital ekonomy, bold new ways for kreator to dey make money online, and many more. Im open to evryone, anywia yu dey for di world - all yu nid na intanet.
page-index-what-is-ethereum-image-alt: Wi dey show pesin wey dey look inside bazaar, wey supose reprisent Ethereum.
page-index-defi-description: Today, plenti pipol nor fit open bank akants, dem don blok oda pipol money. Ethereum desentralize finans (DeFi) system neva sleep abi do pashia. Wit one intanet koneshon, yu fit send, kollet, borrow, chop betta interest, and even dey kollet money from anywia for dis life.
page-index-defi-image-alt: Wi dey show hands wey dey give ETH symbol.
page-index-internet-description: Today, wi gain asess to 'fri' intanet savis if wi surenda awa pesina data. Ethereum savis dey open to evrybody - yu just nid one wallet. Dis na fri and izy way to set up, wey yu dey kontrol, and dey work witout any pesina info.
page-index-internet-button: Make yu yus di open intanet
page-index-internet-image-alt: Wi dey show one fushure komputa set up, wey Ethereum krystals dey run.
page-index-developers-description: Ethereum and im apps dey klear and dey open sorse. Yu fit fork code and yus di funshonality wey odas don already build. If yu nor wont learn new language yu fit just mix wit open sorse code wit Javascript and oda languages wey dey exist.
page-index-developers-code-example-descr: Yu fit build bank wey dey work wit di logik wey yu don program already.
Yu fit kreat tokens wey yu fit transfa and dey yus akross aplikashons.
Yu fit yus di languaj wey exist to mix wit Ethereum and oda aplikashons.
You fit imajin di savis wey dey exist again as disentralize, open aplikashons.
page-index-network-stats-eth-price-expla: Di last price for 1 ether. Yu fit buy as smoll as 0.000000000000000001 - yu nor nid buy di komplit 1 ETH.
page-index-network-stats-total-eth-stake: Di komplit amount of Ethereum wey dem dey stake nau and di one wey dey sikure di netwok.
page-index-network-stats-tx-day-explaine: Di numba of transashons wey dem don susessfully prosess for di netwok for di past 24 hours.
page-index-network-stats-value-defi-desc: Value wey dem lock inside DeFi (USD)
page-index-network-stats-value-defi-expl: Di money for disentralized finans (Defi) aplikashons, di Ethereum digital ekonomy.
page-index-network-stats-nodes-explainer: Na plenti Voluntias around di world dey run Ethereum, wi dem dey koll nodes.
page-index-contribution-banner-descripti: Di website na open sorse wit hundreds of komunity kontributors. Yu fit propose edits to any of di kontent for dis site, wey sujest new tin abi helep us fix some yama-yama bugs.

page-index-contribution-banner-button: More story if you wan contribute
page-index-tout-upgrades-description: The Ethereum roadmap get upgrades wey dey togeda so di netwok go fit dey more sikure, sustainabol and e fit fly.

page-index-tout-enterprise-description: Si hau Ethereum fit take open new biznes models, helep yu riduse smoll kost for yor biznes.
page-index-tout-enterprise-image-alt: Wi dey show komputa wi dey kome in di fushure.
page-index-tout-community-description: Ethereum na about di komunity. Na difrent pipol from difrent place and intrest dey dia. Si hau yu fit join.
page-index-tout-community-image-alt: Wi dey show difrent grup of pipol wey dey wok togeda.
page-index-nft-description: Ethereum nor just dey for digital money oo. Yu fit trade anytin wey yu get if yu put am as (NFTs). Yu fit turn yor work to tokens and get money wen dem resell am. Difrent tins dey hapun all di taim.
page-index-nft-alt: Eth logo wey wi dey yus hologram show.
community-events-content-1: Abeg join us wi don get almost 40 000 membas for awa Discord serva.
community-events-content-2: Make yu show fase for awa evry month komunity kolls for betta update for Ethereum.org divelopment and impotant ecosystem news. Get di shans to ask kweshon, shia idias, and provide feedbak - im bi di pafet oportunity to bi pat of di Ethereum komunity wey dey grow.
